;B[]BL[30]OB[2]TW[ga][ha][ia][sa][ib][sb][rc][sc][sd][ne][se][mf][eg][eh][ei][fj][ql][rm][sm][an][qn][ao][co][qo][ro][so][ap][bp][cp][qp][sp][aq][bq][ar][br][dr][er][as][bs][cs]TB[aa][ca][ma][na][oa][ab][bb][db][mb][ob][ac][bc][ad][bd][cd][dd][ae][be][ce][af][bf][cf][ag][ah][ai][bi][oi][qi][ri][aj][bj][nj][oj][ok][nl][nq][jr][lr][nr][ks][ms][ns][os][ps]C[Kohana [?\]: děkuji za partii
Pig [?\]: diky
